These are Puzzles for 4x4 Level 8

.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-8-1::.
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: aconite, amaryllis, balloon-flower, iris
There are 4 different favourite colors: lavender, fuchsia, mauve, orange
The people have 4 different jobs:  security-guard, mechanic, firefighter, analyst
The people use 4 different means of transport: airplane, jet-ski, motorbike, taxi
 1. the mechanic is not to the right of the security-guard##8
 2. the person driving the airplane is not to the left of the person driving the airplane##8
 3. the person driving the taxi is on the far left or far right##3
 4. the security-guard is not to the left of the analyst##8
 5. the person driving the airplane is not to the right of the person driving the airplane##8
 6. the person who likes mauve is on the right of the analyst##1
 7. the person who growsamaryllis is somewhere to the right of the person who growsaconite##5
 8. the person who likes orange is between the person driving the jet-ski and the mechanic##2
 9. the person driving the taxi is the person who likes mauve##1
10. the person driving the taxi is on the right of the person who growsiris##1
11. the person who growsballoon-flower is on the left or right of the person who likes lavender##3
12. the person who growsiris is somewhere to the right of the person who growsamaryllis##5
13. the person who likes mauve is not to the left of the person driving the taxi##8
14. the person who growsamaryllis is the person driving the motorbike##1
15. the person who growsamaryllis is not the mechanic##6

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2     |      3      |    4    |
| Flower         | aconite     | amaryllis   | iris | balloon-flower |
| Color   | fuchsia | orange   | lavender   | mauve  |
| Job         | mechanic  | firefighter  | analyst  | security-guard |
| Transport     | airplane    | motorbike | jet-ski     | taxi    |

