.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-8-2::.
There are 4 different nationalities: italian, polish, spanish, indonesian
There are 4 different favourite colors: pink, blood-red, purple, ebony
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: house, indie, salsa, trance
House: ranch-style, farmhouse, townhouse, modern
 1. the fan of salsa is between the ranch-style house and the fan of indie##2
 2. the polish is not to the right of the farmhouse house##8
 3. the polish is on the left or right of the person who likes pink##3
 4. the italian is not to the right of the modern house##8
 5. the ranch-style house is not to the left of the fan of indie##8
 6. the person who likes ebony is not to the right of the indonesian##8
 7. the townhouse house is somewhere to the left of the modern house##5
 8. the townhouse house is in an odd position##4
 9. the fan of house is the farmhouse house##1
10. the fan of salsa is on the left or right of the ranch-style house##3
11. the ranch-style house is not to the left of the fan of salsa##8
12. the indonesian is on the left of the polish##1
13. the fan of trance is somewhere to the right of the person who likes blood-red##5
14. the fan of indie is on the left or right of the fan of salsa##3
15. the italian is on the far left or far right##3
16. the person who likes purple is on the right of the person who likes pink##1
17. the italian is not to the right of the fan of indie##8
18. the person who likes blood-red is not to the right of the farmhouse house##8
19. the indonesian is on the right of the person who likes blood-red##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |   2    |   3    |   4   |
| Nationality      | italian | spanish | indonesian  | polish  |
| Color          | ebony     | blood-red | pink | purple  |
| Music-Genre   | indie    | salsa  | trance | house |
| House           | townhouse | modern | ranch-style    | farmhouse  |

