 3. the british is somewhere to the left of the designer##5
 4. the thai is somewhere to the right of the person who's birthday is in may##5
 5. the person who's sport is sailing is not to the right of the electrician##8
 6. the british is not to the left of the journalist##8
 7. the person who's birthday is in january is in an odd position##4
 8. the journalist is on the left of the designer##1
 9. the designer is on the left of the police-officer##1
10. the person who's sport is cycling is on the far right##1
11. the electrician is not to the left of the person who's birthday is in july##8
12. the designer is on the left or right of the person who's sport is cycling##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2     |     3     |     4      |
