 2. the bluemaster-smoker is on the left or right of the person traveling to hannover##3
 3. the person who's birthday is in august is the swisher-smoker##1
 4. the person who's birthday is in may is between the alhambra-smoker and the tiparillo-smoker##2
 5. the person who's hobby is puzzles is on the left or right of the person traveling to prague##3
 6. the person traveling to prague is not to the right of the person who's birthday is in may##8
 7. the person who's hobby is reading is in an odd position##4
 8. the person who's hobby is puzzles is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is board-games##5
 9. the person who's hobby is reading is on the right of the bluemaster-smoker##1
10. the tiparillo-smoker is the person traveling to prague##1
11. the person traveling to boston is not to the right of the person who's birthday is in december##8
12. the alhambra-smoker is on the left or right of the person traveling to boston##3
13. the person who's hobby is puzzles is on the right of the person who's hobby is board-games##1
14. the tiparillo-smoker is on the left or right of the person traveling to boston##3
15. the person who's hobby is board-games is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
