 4. the person who's sport is soccer is not the fan of dubstep##6
 5. the fan of d&b is not to the left of the fan of gospel##8
 6. the person who likes black is somewhere to the left of the person who growsdaisy##5
 7. the person who's sport is soccer is on the left or right of the fan of reggae##3
 8. the person who growsaconite is not to the right of the person who likes black##8
 9. the fan of gospel is somewhere between the person who growsdaisy and the fan of reggae##7
10. the fan of gospel is not to the left of the person who's sport is climbing##8
11. the fan of gospel is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is tennis##5
