 4. the colombian is the wooden house##1
 5. the colonial house is in an even position##4
 6. the person driving the trike is somewhere between the gothic-revival house and the futuristic house##7
 7. the person driving the trike is not to the left of the person driving the taxi##8
 8. the person driving the bus is somewhere between the owner of the bird and the owner of the cat##7
 9. the french is on the far left or far right##3
10. the spanish is not to the left of the spanish##8
11. the french is on the far left##1
12. the turkish is on the far right##1
13. the person driving the trike is the owner of the bird##1
14. the owner of the bird is not to the left of the futuristic house##8
15. the person driving the bus is somewhere to the right of the wooden house##5
16. the spanish is not to the left of the owner of the mouse##8

