.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-8-15::.
The people use 4 different means of transport: subway, train, bus, scooter
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: action, drama, martial-arts, western
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: lily, marigold, sunflower, dahlia
City: berlin, hannover, rome, edinburgh
 1. the person traveling to berlin is the person traveling to berlin##1
