 4. the person traveling to hannover is on the left of the person driving the train##1
 5. the person who growssunflower is on the left or right of the person watching western movies##3
 6. the person driving the scooter is the person driving the scooter##1
 7. the person driving the bus is on the far left##1
 8. the person traveling to berlin is on the left of the person who growsmarigold##1
 9. the person who growssunflower is somewhere to the left of the person watching western movies##5
10. the person watching western movies is on the right of the person traveling to rome##1
11. the person who growsmarigold is on the far left or far right##3
12. the person who growsdahlia is on the left or right of the person watching drama movies##3
13. the person traveling to edinburgh is not to the left of the person driving the subway##8
14. the person driving the train is not to the right of the person driving the scooter##8
15. the person driving the train is the person watching martial-arts movies##1
16. the person driving the bus is not to the right of the person watching western movies##8

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2       |     3     |    4    |
| Transport           | bus | train       | subway      | scooter  |
| Movie-Genre   | action    | martial-arts | western   | drama   |
| Flower   | lily   | sunflower          | dahlia      | marigold  |
| City   | hannover   | rome      | berlin | edinburgh |

