.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-8-16::.
There are 4 different nationalities: thai, british, australian, italian
There 4 different types of food: italianmelon, broccoli, garlic, cranberry
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: climbing, cycling, lacrosse, tennis
4 different games are played: bridge, go, backgammon, whist
 1. the australian is the person who's sport is tennis##1
 2. the person playing go is on the right of the person playing whist##1
 3. the british is somewhere to the right of the person playing whist##5
 4. the thai is on the far left##1
 5. the person playing bridge is on the left or right of the person eating cranberry##3
 6. the person playing backgammon is on the left or right of the person eating garlic##3
 7. the british is on the left or right of the australian##3
 8. the person playing go is not to the right of the person who's sport is cycling##8
 9. the person playing bridge is on the left of the person who's sport is lacrosse##1
10. the british is not to the right of the person eating broccoli##8
11. the person eating garlic is on the right of the italian##1
12. the person playing whist is in an odd position##4
13. the person eating garlic is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is cycling##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |     3      |    4     |
| Nationality      | thai   | italian     | australian    | british |
| Food   | italianmelon  | cranberry      | garlic     | broccoli     |
| Sport         | climbing | lacrosse  | tennis     | cycling  |
| Game     | bridge     | backgammon | whist | go     |

