 4. the person who's birthday is in december is not to the left of the person eating watermelon##8
 5. the person who's birthday is in march is somewhere to the right of the person who's birthday is in january##5
 6. the person who likes black is on the far left or far right##3
 7. the person eating nectarine is somewhere to the left of the person drinking water##5
 8. the person drinking coffee is not to the left of the person who's birthday is in january##8
 9. the person drinking lemonade is on the left or right of the person eating pomegranate##3
10. the person drinking fanta is somewhere between the person who likes grey and the person who's birthday is in february##7
11. the person who likes black is on the left of the person drinking fanta##1

