.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-8-20::.
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: cricket, biathlon, rugby, water-polo
The people have 4 different jobs:  bartender, doctor, social-worker, teacher
There are 4 different favourite colors: purple, blood-red, turquise, yellow
The people use 4 different means of transport: ship, subway, skateboard, airplane
 1. the person who's sport is water-polo is not to the left of the bartender##8
 2. the person who's sport is rugby is on the right of the person who likes turquise##1
 3. the person driving the airplane is somewhere to the right of the person driving the skateboard##5
 4. the teacher is the person who likes yellow##1
 5. the person who's sport is rugby is not the social-worker##6
 6. the person who likes purple is not to the right of the person driving the subway##8
 7. the person who likes blood-red is not to the left of the social-worker##8
 8. the social-worker is on the left or right of the person who's sport is biathlon##3
 9. the person driving the skateboard is in an even position##4
10. the person who likes purple is on the left or right of the person driving the subway##3
11. the person who likes purple is in an even position##4
12. the person who's sport is rugby is between the social-worker and the person who's sport is water-polo##2
13. the person who's sport is water-polo is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2     |       3       |     4      |
| Sport         | water-polo    | rugby   | cricket   | biathlon |
| Job           | bartender | doctor    | social-worker | teacher    |
| Color   | turquise   | purple | blood-red     | yellow    |
| Transport   | ship   | skateboard      | subway         | airplane     |

 